ulturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J. Prag 2017-03-22\" src=\"ISic001834_right-thumb.jpg\"></a></div>  <div id=\"apparatus\"><h4>Apparatus criticus</h4><ul><li><span><span>Text from autopsy</span></span></li></ul></div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2> translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\">  </p><p>of Philisto DB</p>  </div>  <div id=\"commentary\"><h2>commentary</h2>  <p>  </p></div>  <div id=\"bibliography\"><h2>bibliography</h2>  <ul><li> 59.1132 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796</a>  </li><li> De Spuches 1864 13 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002042\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002042</a>  </li><li> Kaibel 1890 <a href=\"https://clio.columbia.edu/catalog/6873760\" target=\"_blank\">437.3</a>  <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072</a>  </li><li> Hoffmann 1904 5233 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000817\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000817</a>  </li><li> Dimartino 2009 722 no. d <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001364\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001364</a>  </li><li> Dimartino 2017 testo d <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002579\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002579</a>  </li></ul>  <ul><li></li></ul>  </div>  <div id=\"handnote\"> <p>Note the lack of serifs and the homogeneity in size of the round letters compared to the others (omicron).</p> <p> Types list: <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Β-type2.html\" target=\"_blank\">Β type2</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Β-type2.1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Β type2.1</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigi